Package: fdic.gov
Title: FDIC BankFind Suite API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the FDIC BankFind Suite API. Search and
    list FDIC-insured institutions, fetch quarterly financial data, bank
    failures, history events, and aggregate banking summaries. No auth required.
